{"tid":120751,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"［世紀大戰上線了］寵物小精靈定數碼暴龍！","createTime":"2017-02-14T16:04:45.000Z","updateTime":"2017-02-15T09:05:27.000Z","uid":50983,"like":22,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"cb10f4b91350d4ccf0cf84ec292bc81f7ad4490c","tid":120751,"uid":50983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-02-14T16:04:45.000Z","msg":"由細到大，同朋友最大嘅矛盾分裂都係源於寵物小精靈同數碼暴龍。大家點睇：<br />\n<br />\n寵物小精靈<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/14/235213_112c46bb863cf5e24349b050360d26fe.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F14%2F235213_112c46bb863cf5e24349b050360d26fe.jpg&h=b3f74bdd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我睇嘅年代都係佢地三個加武藏、小次郎，小精靈都係得百幾隻，後來加咗咩果然翁已經覺得好煩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲有劇情單一，永遠都係喺去道館嘅路程上，我一直都覺得好無聊<br />\n<br />\n數碼暴龍<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/c43w50U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fc43w50U.jpg&h=6b414e1b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/02/14/235533_ef48b80169c10385e130665df7443b8b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F02%2F14%2F235533_ef48b80169c10385e130665df7443b8b.jpg&h=cb0f54fc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n太一同啊古獸真係好正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 被選中嘅小朋友仲有代表唔同特性嘅紋章，進化個bgm又好聽，鼻屎怪又得意<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 不過睇到03打後已經覺得唔好睇，都係01最好j<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n正皮：寵物小精靈（仲會背小精靈圖鑑嘅日子）<br />\n負皮：數碼暴龍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> （03之前）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/offtopic.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 究竟覺得新嘅卡通片唔好睇係我長大咗定真係唔好睇咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ecacde723195ad8de66ac